{"tid":2224729,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［蕭生］5名人士於北角時代冰室進食後懷疑食物中毒！","createTime":"2020-09-30T17:43:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T16:12:36.000Z","uid":219007,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"bd8e95996340f55635bf85eedb76a40fff2fdf54","tid":2224729,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T17:43:25.000Z","msg":"衞生防護中心公佈，正調查兩宗懷疑食物中毒個案，共涉及5人，疑進食蛋類出事。涉事餐廳為時事評論員蕭若元出資營運的黃店、北角英皇道時代冰室，中心呼籲市民保持個人、食物及環境衞生，預防經由食物傳播的疾病。<br />\n<br />\n首宗個案涉及兩男一女，年齡介乎11至62歲。他們在本周日（25日）晚餐時進食購自時代冰室的外賣食物，約7至19小時後出現腹痛、腹瀉、嘔吐及發燒等病徵。另一宗個案涉及兩名17歲男子，他們於同日在冰室午膳，約27至29小時後出現類似病徵。全部受影響人士已求醫，毋須入院接受治療。他們情況穩定。《蘋果》嘗試致電時代冰室查詢，暫未能接通。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心發言人指，衞生署已通知食環署有關事故，並正繼續調查。要預防經由食物傳播的疾病，市民應經常保持個人、食物及環境衞生。在外進食時，應注意食物已徹底煮熟才進食、進食前及如廁後要洗手等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200930/DL64SG2FKRG5DCQVUPZ5RXXTNM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0txi7I9lWatgqOFAQxiLYYL6lZUKewa2WNZnLfsyIMO-GTMdxLvmXLHQY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200930%2FDL64SG2FKRG5DCQVUPZ5RXXTNM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0txi7I9lWatgqOFAQxiLYYL6lZUKewa2WNZnLfsyIMO-GTMdxLvmXLHQY&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kyh4w7aMtX%2B%2FJ%2BUdoe8qorTI%3D&h=601f9dbd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200930%2FDL64SG2FKRG5DCQVUPZ5RXXTNM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0txi7I9lWatgqOFAQxiLYYL6lZUKewa2WNZnLfsyIMO-GTMdxLvmXLHQY&h=5dd12ec3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200930/DL64SG2FKRG5DCQVUPZ5RXXTNM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0txi7I9lWatgqOFAQ